# 📚 Book Finder App

A simple book search application built with **React** and the **Open Library API**.  
This project allows users to search books by title, view book details, and open a preview page.

---

## 🚀 Features
- 🔍 Search books by title  
- 📖 Display book covers, title, and author  
- 🔎 Preview button links to Open Library book page  
- 🎨 Responsive card layout with clean UI  

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- **Framework:** React  
- **Styling:** Inline CSS (can be extended to Tailwind / CSS Modules)  
- **Data Fetching:** Open Library API (no auth required)  
- **State Management:** React Hooks (`useState`)  

---

## 📦 Installation

Clone the repository and install dependencies:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/book-finder-app.git
cd book-finder-app
npm install
npm start


src/
 ├── App.js        # Main React component
 ├── index.js      # Entry point
 └── ...
